{"tid":1462331,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"集合一班手足勸前面唔好阻旅客好無","createTime":"2019-08-13T10:23:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T14:53:27.000Z","uid":201310,"like":24,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"217c4b4089a835e86e0fed55fb8dd8e74b841153","tid":1462331,"uid":201310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:23:26.000Z","msg":"我一路喺現場 由阻旅客開始我已經見到好多旅客好燥底 <br />\n既然今日咁少人 就唔應阻旅客登機 簡單諗下比人阻既係自己就會明白佢地感受<br />\n<br />\n我知道現場有手足都唔想因為今日而失去外國既輿論民意 但又未必夠膽自己一個企起身講 因為我就係 <br />\n所以有無手足一齊勸下前面？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aj9h4o0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAj9h4o0.png&h=c4a1529b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed478698ddbe06bc9a9014a6772562d84fe573b0","tid":1462331,"uid":201310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:23:32.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"e5a0ed9e231003f20f4e8a86cf48b179b0230c0a","tid":1462331,"uid":201310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:23:44.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"1db5788d4726c58157e0d2eb55472a5f721d59ab","tid":1462331,"uid":201310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:23:58.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"a78c1911b42c591452765cc89ab182ad432ade7f","tid":1462331,"uid":201310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:24:27.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"c7f1477786dc7e5b4811d7064a93b0f3113aa099","tid":1462331,"uid":201310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:24:43.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"972017e435e3eb2ce40b5fec11b01882cfefb061","tid":1462331,"uid":285371,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:24:47.000Z","msg":"阻旅客上機<br />\n外國人番到hometown 會話班示威者搞事<br />\n香港政府做得岩<br />\n佢上唔到機而班機無取消 <br />\n係咪你賠比個班旅客<br />\n<br />\n你和平集會 多人塞到路<br />\n機場自然會cancel 班機<br />\n航空公司同香港機場賠錢<br />\n班旅客屌政府多過示威者<br />\n<br />\n一開始去機場集會既意義<br />\n係向國際宣傳我地被政府迫害<br />\n狗行使武力<br />\n依家變成屌旅客阻旅客"},{"pid":"4efea8