 style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">搵出影響力最大嘅時間</span></strong></span><br />\n睇下邊段時間<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">最多人能響應</span></span></strong>，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">找出平衡</span></span></strong><br />\n然後用<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">隔日形式塞爆</span></span></strong><br />\n能節省大家金錢同時間去再去<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最大化個運動成效</span></span></strong><br />\n隔日嘅好處係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">避免大家過勞和積累</span></strong>過多<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">外國民怨</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>個人認為呢位師兄言之有物<br />\n希望大家可以集思廣益</strong></span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n[理性討論] 有死線前提搞機場/隔日搞機場比日日搞更好 | LIHKG<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1459515/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1459515/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我地團結一致</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\nPush"},{"pid":"c1e009861ffa4e566089a29bf06c0d7f911f774b","tid":1462331,"uid":210489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:27:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"38e7a15b4539a682a59a972c3cc36142b5b4dd82","tid":1462331,"uid":16458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:27:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"99fd174ea99242bb8e53a126374b92e1a947af86","tid":1462331,"uid":16458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"972017e435e3eb2ce40b5fec11b01882cfefb061","tid":1462331,"uid":285371,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:24:47.000Z","msg":"阻旅客上機<br />\n外國人番到hometown 會話班示威者搞事<br />\n香港政府做得岩<br />\n佢上唔到機而班機無取消 <br />\n係咪你賠比個班旅客<br />\n<br />\n你和平集會 多人塞到路<br />\n機場自然會cancel 班機<br />\n航空公司同香港機場賠錢