19-08-13T10:29:41.000Z","msg":"人少去塞, 咪同地鐵不合作運動一樣, 專登阻頭阻勢, 犯眾憎囉.<br />\n人多坐哂係度, D旅客最多都只有無奈, 我又唔係專登阻住你, 人多都冇計架.<br />\n<br />\n各有各做啦, 可以討論下, 但冇得拉佢地走既. 佢地慢慢番去諗清楚會改良個做法. 大家都睇到比左咁多意見, 地鐵不合作運動少左, 係咪? 我相信大家有獨立思考同埋進步既能力. 呢樣亦都係我地比政府優勝既地方."},{"pid":"1cca75ee7cbf0bbb3f17974328defa72458a85b3","tid":1462331,"uid":157653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c37c5c42482348429d847078adfb773c46d60b3c","tid":1462331,"uid":200389,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:28:22.000Z","msg":"勿忘初衷 唔好浪費咁多位手足係機場對外國遊客做咗咁多日宣傳嘅心血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:29:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5420cdb66ef7eaa1ae1f141cf80c7aa3e970f715","tid":1462331,"uid":4001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:30:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">放核彈都唔割</span>"},{"pid":"212d8282df0f4ff25632ce4c096219780168e4f3","tid":1462331,"uid":258956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:31:15.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"c8ff82ff094c1638139c6c7a7ec24eba49ef5911","tid":1462331,"uid":31491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:31:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d15c69f527cf7f25324d4fa0c0f0a3f2e85c1e87","tid":1462331,"uid":282981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:31:23.000Z","msg":"仲有專登阻人阻門口, 保安警察有權做野, 如果同人打起交上來, 警察更加可以做野! 到時一大班人送頭.<br />\n<br />\n你坐係度, 冇人有權做野."},{"pid":"a234ff20bc17f93439c8a2a19ab0c747415ded28","tid":1462331,"uid":201310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:31:36.000Z","msg":"機場我一路都有去 接機果陣睇得出外國旅客大部分係支持 <br />\n<br />\n況且<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">宜家唔係叫你地唔好塞 係叫大家喺夠人既情況塞 係都要話人政治潔癖左膠</span>"},{"pid":"02069e3a1b1f97aba5c91cba2dcfbd8e17793868","tid":1462331,"uid":242728,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:32:26.000Z","msg":"我明白人數唔多<br />\n但係機場搞不合作好難眾人心<br />\n尤其你想打國際牌<br />\n<br />\n請各位三思<br />\n心急行錯路就會斷送一切的努力<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">各位手足我地已經入緊黎，請冷靜</span>"},{"pid":"47f8e580834b2f376e02b1b93b0010e495549241","tid":1462331,"uid":59644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:33:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2af98127cd240d879fb819f1c1605c6a320ee7f8","tid":1462331,"uid":41507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cca75ee7cbf0bbb3f17974328defa72458a85b3","tid":1462331,"uid":157653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c37c5c42482348429d847078adfb773c46d60b3c","tid":1462331,"uid":200389,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:28:22.000Z","msg":"勿忘初衷 唔好浪費咁多位手足係機場對外國遊客做咗咁多日宣傳嘅心血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:29:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:33:54.000Z","msg":"鬼嘜撚野 咪撚成日分化啦"},{"pid":"2842c522032c1bb9d4e5174956c055072972d7c5","tid":1462331,"uid":200389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5420cdb66ef7eaa1ae1f141cf80c7aa3e970f715","tid":1462331,"uid":4001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:30:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">放核彈都唔割</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:34:21.000Z","msg":"唔係要割 只係建議 大家都想贏"},{"pid":"71ed02f50d4dc5b7e9c802676f4683c00bedd88f","tid":1462331,"uid":114750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:34:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/2014/new/oct/2/images/bigPic/600_157.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2F2014%2Fnew%2Foct%2F2%2Fimages%2FbigPic%2F600_157.jpg&h=c0500713&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20141001/large/1412115210_69e4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20141001%2Flarge%2F1412115210_69e4.jpg&h=02c8d847&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咪咁?"},{"pid":"b628b65415ff348bee4d63fa4553554e7470f6e9","tid":1462331,"uid":202375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:34:31.000Z","msg":"真心唔好阻住旅客 唔好打擾佢地<br />\n佢地唔係我地既目標<br />\n阻住佢上機冇意思 只會失民意<br />\n要取消既機佢地會自動取消念頭入禁區<br />\n<br />\n可能有popo 係做鬼帶大家封會地<br />\n咁就有藉口比政府話示威者擾民 比子彈政府<br />\n<br />\nAnyway 各有各做 <br />\n係主流意見話要block 佢地既話我冇野講<br />\n多數服從少數<br />\n<br />\nBe water，不割"},{"pid":"a4277bdfe826b0c339dae948c4e1c732e6928005","tid":1462331,"uid":201310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:35:08.000Z","msg":"各位手足慎重考慮 建議唔阻入口既人唔一定係鬼同左膠 我地一定要揀啱時機再塞 <br />\n機場仲有外國媒體報道 設身處地諗下你係外國人 求其lap下新聞見到標題寫hk示威者阻住遊客 都知道宜家暫時成個觀感都唔係好 不割席但都不魯莽"},{"pid":"216e3359262e4ba65a94da5c1d816d1a0c2a8ac9","tid":1462331,"uid":201310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71ed02f50d4dc5b7e9c802676f4683c00bedd88f","tid":1462331,"uid":114750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:34:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/2014/new/oct/2/images/bigPic/600_157.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2F2014%2Fnew%2Foct%2F2%2Fimages%2FbigPic%2F600_157.jpg&h=c0500713&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20141001/large/1412115210_69e4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20141001%2Flarge%2F1412115210_69e4.jpg&h=02c8d847&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咪咁?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:35:34.000Z","msg":"佢地有無阻住外國旅客？"},{"pid":"c63a376578e3f8bd44e0a3335837ec13e7dc15db","tid":1462331,"uid":249187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"972017e435e3eb2ce40b5fec11b01882cfefb061","tid":1462331,"uid":285371,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:24:47.000Z","msg":"阻旅客上機<br />\n外國人番到hometown 會話班示威者搞事<br />\n香港政府做得岩<br />\n佢上唔到機而班機無取消 <br />\n係咪你賠比個班旅客<br />\n<br />\n你和平集會 多人塞到路<br />\n機場自然會cancel 班機<br />\n航空公司同香港機場賠錢<br />\n班旅客屌政府多過示威者<br />\n<br />\n一開始去機場集會既意義<br />\n係向國際宣傳我地被政府迫害<br />\n狗行使武力<br />\n依家變成屌旅客阻旅客"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:35:59.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9a76a5f897f360b7d9561426d69f5a71be43b30","tid":1462331,"uid":200389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:37:03.000Z","msg":"國際對我地嘅睇滋好重要 好撚多外國記者影住"},{"pid":"00e80f45ed9547e6f6ee53ee56f2cb18d0a1a87b","tid":1462331,"uid":157653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2af98127cd240d879fb819f1c1605c6a320ee7f8","tid":1462331,"uid":41507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cca75ee7cbf0bbb3f17974328defa72458a85b3","tid":1462331,"uid":157653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c37c5c42482348429d847078adfb773c46d60b3c","tid":1462331,"uid":200389,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:28:22.000Z","msg":"勿忘初衷 唔好浪費咁多位手足係機場對外國遊客做咗咁多日宣傳嘅心血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:29:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:33:54.000Z","msg":"鬼嘜撚野 咪撚成日分化啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:37:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"028e6bff2b0d9a4514a4fc3161ddaa690863bc9d","tid":1462331,"uid":4001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"216e3359262e4ba65a94da5c1d816d1a0c2a8ac9","tid":1462331,"uid":201310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71ed02f50d4dc5b7e9c802676f4683c00bedd88f","tid":1462331,"uid":114750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T